{"tid":1916473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［大清算］Android機問題？出賣定位","createTime":"2020-03-09T01:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T02:30:22.000Z","uid":260292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab5c72cfd31bfdacdff0bd2ae59389b4ac3e8d2","tid":1916473,"uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:45:00.000Z","msg":"借ac<br />\n小弟今朝一如既往del record，由細到大用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Android機</span></span>，多年用同一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">google ac</span></span>，del極都覺得自己del得唔乾淨，於是返公司用電腦開google setting睇下，一睇就hihi，原來我手機del極電腦都睇到啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問非it人，只係求其㩒己經睇到自己幾時去過邊，search過咩。我一向都有熄location習慣，只係開google map有陣先會開左定位，雖然話係我手機狂del record下4月以後紀錄冇晒，但佢連我幾年前去左邊到旅行都mark左我。奇怪位：同事用iPhone從來冇del record ，一開卻完全0紀錄超新淨。<br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求求大家唔好懶，求其都<strong>用電腦開</strong>黎睇下自己乾唔乾淨</span></span>，佢邊啲mark邊啲唔mark真係好難捉摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/goYs6QS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgoYs6QS.jpg&h=8852995a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebac0bbd7aa540cf585ea94eec5487a0978372c7","tid":1916473,"uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:45:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20906bc66e85c3f148434a58924b2a6769520427","tid":1916473,"uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:45:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"57e5b47cb5d9c65801e47d4206514f89cf478934","tid":1916473,"uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:45:36.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a19cd2d2809b6f4e5d5141c8808db3dd528827ec","tid":1916473,"uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ac130892ab6b3126c74c21f12e706f96c3019d43","tid":